Agent steht im Raum mit Begrüßung:
"Hello and Welcome to MedicineVR!" -> Standardtext des Tooltips

Später würde durch einen Button ermöglicht werden, die Einführung zu starten.
Momentan reicht es, wenn der Agent ca. 10 Sekunden wartet und dann Anfängt.

"Firstly, let me introduce myself: I am Doctor ..., your guide through this fascinating journey of the human body!" -> 10 Sekunden Speech task

Geht zum Herz -> eventuell Geste/AdaptiveGaze/Zeigen
"Let's start with the heart. This incredible organ is like the engine of your body, pumping blood and keeping you alive." -> 10 Sekunden Speech Task
"It works tirelessly to distribute blood throughout your entire system." 6 Sekunden Speech Task

Geht zum Gehirn -> eventuell Geste/AdaptiveGaze/Zeigen
"Next, we have the brain. Think of it as the control center, managing everything from your thoughts to your movements."  -> 10 Sekunden Speech Task
"It is part of our nerve system and very important for regulating our body, while also giving us consciousness. How Awesome!" -> 10 Sekunden Speech Task

Geht zur Leber -> eventuell Geste/AdaptiveGaze/Zeigen
"Here we have the liver, a powerhouse of metabolism." -> 5 Sekunden Speech Task
"It processes nutrients and produces essential proteins. It also breaks down and excretes substances. Truly indispensable!" -> 10 Sekunden Speech Task

Geht zur Lunge -> eventuell Geste/AdaptiveGaze/Zeigen
"And finally, the lungs." -> 3 Sekunden Speech Task
"They draw in oxygen and expel carbon dioxide, keeping your blood oxygenated and your body functioning." -> 9 Sekunden Speech Task

Stellt sich in die Mitte der Zylinder:
"You can SELECT any organ by clicking it to learn more about it." -> 1 Sekunde Speech Task (Text bleibt sowieso erhalten)
